{"tid":2219453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"令人失望的一件事","createTime":"2020-09-27T01:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T02:09:12.000Z","uid":284669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c41a00c6b8f78c8f90145fec778094dbeb315bde","tid":2219453,"uid":284669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:24:24.000Z","msg":"8月底在Telegram谷見到有手足賣銷匙扣，一套三款$190，出於幫手足，買了一套，在FPS轉了$190給他，後來他說其實中一款無貨，要遲幾日，話唔好意思，我仲好有耐心好有禮貌咁叫佢唔好俾自己咁大壓力，好小事啫，你下星期update我啦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n之後幾個星期我到已經忘記了這事。<br />\n<br />\n幾日前再想起（已經足足一個月），再WhatsApp問佢，已經無回應，message無變雙藍剔，好可能已經無再用該號碼。<br />\n<br />\n$190小事，但破壞了手足互信，令人失望。這樣的品格操守，對得起這場抗爭嗎？<br />\n<br />\n*電話尾數8450，大家不要再中伏。"},{"pid":"10a88de7fdc7fc20d14ebba8f9d5b10a1f1a092f","tid":2219453,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d611ab66c48db8f3d6275d73d9935f8b7f35888f","tid":2219453,"uid":284669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a88de7fdc7fc20d14ebba8f9d5b10a1f1a092f","tid":2219453,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"我少發文，仍然是P牌"},{"pid":"d7b8c1091bc90befac326cd761bbffd181ec64c0","tid":2219453,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a88de7fdc7fc20d14ebba8f9d5b10a1f1a092f","tid":2219453,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:26:54.000Z","msg":"P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:30:52.000Z","msg":"p牌又點?上連登時間長短=講真/假?"},{"pid":"77a88a329032d279b38128044286769f109a24ae","tid":2219453,"uid":368660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"樓主幫手足去旁聽好過,順便直接俾錢手足"},{"pid":"5d1fc9270847314379136be7fd0d73af7ac7e01b","